headline.main: Alabama City Re-enacts March That Sparked 'Bloody Sunday'
headline.print_headline: Alabama City Re-enacts March That Sparked 'Bloody Sunday'

lead_paragraph: Throngs of people converged in the city of Selma, Alabama, for the annual re-enactment of a key event in the civil rights movement.
